    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的。特别要注意的是，STREAMING状态内部有循环——ActuatorController每发送一帧都会进入pending ACK的状态，这是关键的重传机制。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "STREAMING",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
