      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经画出了从HANDSHAKING到STREAMING的双触发路径。现在处理STREAMING到DRAINING的转换——这是优雅关闭的流程吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
